    H=  1: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [0, 0], expected (H-1)/2 = 0
    H=  3: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [1, 1], expected (H-1)/2 = 1
    H=  5: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [2, 2], expected (H-1)/2 = 2
    H=  9: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [4, 4], expected (H-1)/2 = 4
    H= 11: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [5, 5], expected (H-1)/2 = 5
    H= 13: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [6, 6], expected (H-1)/2 = 6
    H= 15: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [7, 7], expected (H-1)/2 = 7
    H= 17: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [8, 8], expected (H-1)/2 = 8
    H= 19: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [9, 9], expected (H-1)/2 = 9
    H= 23: β₁+2β₂ ∈ [11, 11], expected (H-1)/2 = 11
